name: Hummingbird
content: I was sad and feeling down
Then one day she came around
This little bird made me see
All I needed was a little friend
我所需要的是一个朋友
Wish you could stay with me forever
希望你能永远和我在一起
Night and day we'd be together
Come sing my song my little hummingbird
来唱我的歌我的小蜂鸟
Come sing along my little hummingbird
来唱我的歌我的小蜂鸟
Always makes me feel so tough
I feel good when she is near
当她靠近时候我感觉好多了
